parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch system can cause the vehicle to lose gear engagement, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle cannot shift into or out of gear while running
the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended movement of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The vehicle moves out of "park" without warning
the vehicle rolls away
the vehicle hits another object or vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The erratic behavior of the brake system can cause accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly slows down without warning
the RBS/ABS system starts slowing the car on its own
the vehicle is difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning brake system can cause unpredictable braking behavior, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The brakes stop too hard or drag when pressing the pedal
making it difficult to control the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning odometer can lead to inaccurate mileage readings, affecting the vehicle's maintenance and resale value.
symptoms: The miles odometer flashes
indicating a faulty reading.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fracture and detachment of door handles can cause difficulty or impossibility in opening or closing the doors, which can lead to inconvenience, safety risks, and potential accidents.
symptoms: The door handles break or detach from the inner side of the handle
making it difficult or impossible to open or close the doors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the mirror mount can cause the mirror to detach, obstructing the driver's view and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The mirror pops off or becomes loose
obstructing the driver's view.
